GameConfig - Class in com.mygdx.game.model
GameConfig is a class that keeps information about the configuration of the level, such has the depth of the level and the number of enemies in it.
GameConfig(int, int) - Constructor for class com.mygdx.game.model.GameConfig
Constructor that set the depth and number of enemies of the level to the ones given (minimum difficulty).
GameController - Class in com.mygdx.game.controller
GameController class controls everything related to the physics of the game.
GameController(GameModel) - Constructor for class com.mygdx.game.controller.GameController
Constructor that fill the physics world with the bodies of the game entities, given by the GameModel.
GameModel - Class in com.mygdx.game.model
GameModel class deals with the construction of all the entities that make the game, such as the map, the enemies, the hero, the stats, the sound and the game configuration.
